*尊敬的演員是{{link-ja|大瀧秀治|大滝秀治}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/7184557/|title=″本物の俳優″を目指す阿部寛「50歳まであと2年、あせりますよ」|publisher=HAPPY PLUS（ハピプラ）（livedoor NEWS）|date=2012-11-29|accessdate=2014-01-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140112152533/http://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/7184557/|archivedate=2014-01-12}}</ref>，兩人終於在《{{link-ja|最後的律師|最後の弁護人}}》共演。
